<template>
  <button @click="addCounter">{{ counterValue }}</button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: "GlobalComponent",
    props: ['initialTest'],
    data(){
        return {
            counterValue: this.initialTest
        }
    },
    methods: {
        addCounter(){
            this.counterValue += 2
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
